;   :on-tick step-world
;   :on-key handle-input
;   :render draw-scene)
; ```
; 
; **Emergent behavior:** playable game.
; 
; ---
; 
; ### 19.5 `sprite/*`, `audio/*` — Row 5 (composition tier)
; 
; **Base:** sprite audio.
; 
; **Composition example:** composed give footstep sync.
; 
; ```scheme
